{"tid":1276680,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再講撤回條例啦","createTime":"2019-07-02T04:20:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T04:20:03.000Z","uid":88767,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d777fdc233235acc1fe2e7e9d97f4c96877512d1","tid":1276680,"uid":88767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:20:03.000Z","msg":"唔係話撤回唔重要 係有其他比佢更重要<br />\n一日條賊婆想重啟二讀 <br />\n我相信今時今日既香港人好多會肯再企出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我認為衣加係既首要目標係 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">追究警權過大 無條件釋放義士</span></span><br />\n我覺得呢兩個先係當務之急<br />\n設立 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">獨立委員會</span></span><br />\n搵返曬所有有開槍既警犬 一個都不能放過！！<br />\n不能任由佢地恰示威者<br />\n一定要搵人出來祭旗！ 還烈士心願！！<br />\n至於其他撤回條例 林鄭下台 <br />\n係重要 但無以上2點重點<br />\n義士們一個都不能少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申:呢兩日發夢係咁喊 聽到好多人話好絶望 所以我地更加要一步步推呢個極權政府做d野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}